Definition: an opinion formed beforehand without adequate evidence
Example: he did not even try to confirm his preconceptions
Synonyms: verb, creation, preconceive, prepossession, cognition, prepossess, parti_pris, preconceived_opinion, preconceived_idea, preconceived_notion, opinion, an, formed, beforehand, without, adequate, evidence, he, did, not, even, try, to, confirm, his, preconceptions
Category: noun.cognition
